5 Iranians Killed , 10 Injured in Explosion
TEHRAN , December 28 ( Xinhua ) -- An explosion occurred on a fuel tanker of the Iranian navy Sunday afternoon , killing five crew members and injured 10 others .
So far the reason for the incident has not been established .
The tanker anchored at the naval forces jetty in the southern port Bandar Abass , the Islamic Republic News Agency ( IRNA ) reported on Monday .
The injured , who suffered burns , have been sent to hospital and the fire has been extinguished .
